definitions.definition: A town in Staffordshire , England ( OS grid ref SK2203 ) .
A local government district with borough status of Staffordshire with its headquarters in the town.
A city and administrative centre of Tamworth Regional Council in New South Wales , Australia .
A local government area in northern New South Wales ; in full, Tamworth Regional Council .
A town in Carroll County , New Hampshire , United States .
A hamlet in Cumberland County , Virginia , United States .
A community in Stone Mills , Lennox and Addington County , Ontario , Canada .

definitions.definition: One of a long-established English breed of large pigs . They are red, often spotted with black, with a long snout and erect or forward-pointed ears, and are valued for bacon production.
